Usage: addChannelDensityControl [-help] <llx> <lly> <urx> <ury> <layer> <ratio>

-help                # Prints out the command usage
<llx>                # llx (float, required)
<lly>                # lly (float, required)
<urx>                # urx (float, required)
<ury>                # ury (float, required)
<layer>              # layer name (string, required)
<ratio>              # ratio (float, required, min=0, max=1)